{"tid":2133762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再多118宗本地確診個案　新增直銷公司群組","createTime":"2020-07-31T09:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T11:06:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"623762119d3d0ac628683cff27cac44539f6fef9","tid":2133762,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:31:06.000Z","msg":"本地個案中，62宗與早前個案相關，當中48宗屬於親友聚會。今日新增何文田怡安閣「Star Global」直銷公司感染群組，至今有6人確診及5人初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君說，公司主要進行直銷及人手培訓，地庫有售賣紅酒及化妝品，能容納100人，擔心有更多人感染，部分員工星期一曾到去太子利美大廈培訓，直銷場地目前已關閉消毒，員工可能要接受檢疫，警方亦已協助追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n她說，堅城梁氏建築公司在觀塘創紀之城11樓的辦公室再多1人感染，大廈1名曾清潔同層洗手間的清潔工亦確診，群組累計涉及25人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541056-20200731.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541056-20200731.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1xYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ebf979cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541056-20200731.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=64c559c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541056-20200731.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1d5260e32e3a19d6bc8b8eb1bd27db8da3dad058","tid":2133762,"uid":54511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直銷 病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87be502370627b1fcfc9f14bbfc126592c0a252","tid":2133762,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"傳銷撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3748760d178041fc8768f0e81f23c19f82da13","tid":2133762,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0